➜猫以高难度的姿势睡觉真的舒服吗？
https://daily.zhihu.com/story/9726399	83244
<div><div><div>
<img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-38bfedba3ee7ba2c0317bbdf06a16105_is.jpg">
<span>猫研所，</span><span>猫咪知识精准科普平台</span>
<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/406041144/answer/1366411967" hidden>阅读原文</a>
</div><div>
<p>所长认为<strong>应该是舒服的，不然不会睡得那么香~</strong></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c7ddf4a6d11dfa80a698fad6db218586_b.jpg" alt=""><figcaption>图自网络</figcaption></figure><p>众所周知，<strong>猫咪是“液体”，所以在我们看来极其别扭的姿势，对猫咪来说是再正常不过的了。</strong></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d5c7347a567713b654768bf8dc9c590b_b.jpg" alt=""><figcaption>图自网络</figcaption></figure><p>那么问题来了，猫咪为什么可以那么灵活？</p><p><strong><strong>因为，猫咪天生骨骼精奇！</strong></strong></p><p>和我们常识不同的是：“液体猫”们非但不是像软体动物那样“柔若无骨”，反倒有着比人类更多的骨头。</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8bce8732af644a041e89a6749881cd00_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><p>但不要误会，能不能把身体拧成逆天的姿势绝不是靠数量上取胜。<strong>躯干骨的构造才是哺乳动物们能够自由控制身体伸缩这方面起关键作用。</strong></p><ul><li><strong>嵴 柱</strong></li></ul><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1ecc70e301cf9624ba619a58e20f499e_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><p>猫嵴柱的构造使它们可以在任何一个方向上将它们的身体<strong>旋转 180 度。</strong></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f52e4d667facd90fb8ef494d0e8d5703_b.jpg" alt=""><figcaption>图自：awkwardfamilyphotos</figcaption></figure><p>猫的嵴柱在空中可以朝各个方向扭转，让他们<strong>迅速保持向上的姿势。</strong></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2998fd62cb495dfb54236445cf25362f_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption>旋转跳跃我不闭眼。图自：Giphy </figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2251a3d135688843233dc6998c4b64ba_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption> 够你丫的！图自：Giphy</figcaption></figure><p>人嵴柱的构造使躯干可以旋转大约 90 度。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5bbe1b140087d99cf2bd505e7494f4dd_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption>图自：Giphy</figcaption></figure><ul><li><strong>肋 骨</strong></li></ul><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f3d3b56423f76e96bd368594007f3496_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f18ce9b46825520bfeacc1b3f021f721_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption> 图自：Giphy </figcaption></figure><p>猫肋骨的结构使<strong>胸廓又深而狭窄</strong>，这利于胸骨压缩，使身体变细变软，更容易通过狭窄的地方。</p><p>人的胸廓是左右径大于前后径的扁宽形状，起到支撑保护心肺等重要脏器的作用。</p><ul><li><strong>肩胛骨</strong></li></ul><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-821ff5f9e7b510e993caba1ba06e206d_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><p>猫的肩胛骨结构方便它们出入狭小的空间。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d35a61dd1558cc4cd6d8c831918e012d_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption> 图自：Giphy</figcaption></figure><p>人的肩胛骨结构使人手臂以圆形方式旋转或铰接向外和向上远离身体的运动。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f93483ead6389d07a16cc6fc4edae202_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption> 图自：Giphy</figcaption></figure><ul><li><strong>锁 骨</strong></li></ul><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-269b1efbc1b632e292714f5ddcd07ecd_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><p>猫咪<strong>浮动的锁骨</strong>使得它们更容易在狭小的穿梭</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d16acd4fa42233f2f8e5d3a4025c3125_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption> 图自：Giphy</figcaption></figure><p>也更方便它们使用终极秘笈——<strong>喵喵拳</strong></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79b783149188cb39ce1f487b2564e410_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption>图自：Giphy</figcaption></figure><p>人的锁骨支撑肩胛骨，使上肢骨与胸廓保持一定距离，利于上肢的灵活运动。</p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-76fe1a4abde7cdc980d3d8b78820296b_b.gif" alt=""><figcaption>图自：Giphy</figcaption></figure><p>总的说来，在野外生存中，猫是孤独的猎食者。作为食肉动物的它们需要面对更多危险，也需要更高的效率。</p><p>因此<strong>猫的骨骼使猫趋于灵活，并有助于快速爆发及伏击躲避。当然，在把自己拧成麻花这方面，猫咪也有得天独厚的优势。</strong></p><p><strong>下面就请进入猫咪的奇葩睡姿大赏~</strong></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-75cdfe82b3d18ade480508b468e30bf8_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0841c512e79dc6ea38a8fd586845f343_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-03abd01fc590588b09daceb745af381b_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c2a90bbb894812708bf768e13a5f435e_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8d0fd098cf7bff8a246ef210d568af81_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-81400780f1b219972ea04a81e5405041_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4431bbf84e6903905cf73edef50f7b6c_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4e7060ec97d57afb4d5168e20fa486ed_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ef2895d0cb6a10e1d77655a77c426acb_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e793c6f8d45a6ae7c2aa761bf3cbfe6e_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9781561319a99b3e2928d352889a97ab_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-09f989b0f435016e0ac544aa4875cc48_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-186e79c8a4c446c77c7bb889188824a6_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-781a93020e6cf5276d1833a6d41ded24_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2b97ecbb3574caadb6c33e748bd13864_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d7699167b8b8a3ce8725592b196f2a87_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ec68ce89b9ea62f5d2a8bede1e133a7e_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1ada4a06f3d2fb1bfee281f758ec9897_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-807cfddc10538cfda578ada5bf05086f_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b7cd72f17752234cf91f8ef97a22ff14_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b7a44734a1f9112375aae39006a5f815_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-96c275e3c64b5085a64508982e578f4c_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-98a2bd07cbc5cb47583e473335e2ecda_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-eeb6246ecc7e7ce981a6838e506cc4b1_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9fc37964206dbf12b56166c63fa086a6_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-064066f568f5c47f30760a9a63a75e5b_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b11444a994c2a7cba6268966dc56d4db_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-41c7dcbe8f7906cf3a1312577ec44ed6_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c834b69b8544f53b659cd6e1fe24c431_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-86ac03cc7858f5d7b9b4a68db0497293_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9416c312ba3ed7e2597dce8a3d74d48b_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8f204438d3dbe4addde6fd634875b846_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3312c08e0b6a5447bae4b710c413d520_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-77e39c812fa6b53370c07e6bb3e61bb9_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b59c7eb28d2722e5621f7295cb64702e_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f7775b9543d9bbb8edb11ac90a8a8f04_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9b248d05a22f7121990ff160ba9bee4a_b.jpg" alt=""></figure><p>以上图片均来自：boredpanda。</p><hr><p>参考资料：</p><p>[1]Michael A. Foss, DVM, Skamania County; Nancy Stewart, King County; and Jean Swift,Skagit County. Cat Anatomy and Physiology. [M]:Washington State University Extension [2008]</p><p>[2]Stephen G. Gilbert ,Cheralea Gilbert.Outline of Cat Anatomy with Reference to the Human[M] University of Washington Press.[2000]</p><p>[3]<a href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//sciencing.com/comparison-human-cat-skeleton-6495829.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span>https://</span><span>sciencing.com/compariso</span><span>n-human-cat-skeleton-6495829.html</span><span></span></a></p>
